  <item>
    <title>2016 Workshop on Collaborative Data Projects（開放報名）</title>
    <link>http://creativecommons.tw/blog/20161208</link>
    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot; property=&quot;content:encoded&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;The 2016 Workshop on Collaborative Data Projects will be held on December 8, 2016&amp;nbsp;at Academia Sinica in Taipei.&amp;nbsp;The purpose of this workshop is to call on the attention of the wider research community to share best practices in collaborative data projects, to discuss common issues, and to propose directions for actions.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;「2016 資料協作專案工作坊」將於 12&amp;nbsp;月 8&amp;nbsp;日在台北中央研究院舉行。舉行此工作坊，希望能引發廣泛研究社群的注意，分享資料協作的實務方法，討論共同面對的議題，並一起提出行動的方向。&lt;/p&gt;
